Sentencas: The particle size distribution and the specific surface area of yttria stabilized zirconia (YSZ) powders could be changed by pre-calcining.
Titulo: Effects of pre-calcined YSZ powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anodes for SOFC

Sentencas: Accordingly, the performances of Ni-YSZ cermet might be changed too.
Titulo: Effects of pre-calcined YSZ powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anodes for SOFC

Sentencas: In this paper, the effects of pre-calcined YSZ powders on Ni-YSZ cermet were investigated.
Titulo: Effects of pre-calcined YSZ powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The performances of Ni-YSZ cermet, including the basic physical characterization, sintering shrinkage and electrochemical properties, were studied in connection with the quality of YSZ powders pre-calcined at 900 degrees C, 1100 degrees C and 1200 degrees C, respectively.
Titulo: Effects of pre-calcined YSZ powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The results indicated that the crystal structure was not changed, but the porosity of open holes in NiO-YSZ pellets was increased with the pre-calcining temperature increasing.
Titulo: Effects of pre-calcined YSZ powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anodes for SOFC

Sentencas: In addition, the total shrinkage of different anode materials was changed by using different YSZ powders, the value of Ni-YSZ cermet doping with YSZ pre-calcined at 900 degrees C and 1100 degrees C was closer to that of YSZ electrolyte.
Titulo: Effects of pre-calcined YSZ powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anodes for SOFC

Sentencas: The cermet with YSZ powders pre-calcined at 900 degrees C showed the highest electric conductivity, and its polarization performance was closed to that of cermet with raw YSZ powders.
Titulo: Effects of pre-calcined YSZ powders at different temperatures on Ni-YSZ anodes for SOFC
